{"id":72125,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/05/google向社会公开招聘社交媒体业务主管/","date":"2010-05-13T05:40:11Z","modified":"2010-05-13T05:40:11Z","title":"Google向社会公开招聘社交媒体业务主管","content":"<p>其实Google在社交媒体上做得已经非常不错了，他们有<a href=\"http://www.google.com/press/blogs/directory.html\">官方博客群</a>，近百个<a href=\"http://www.google.com/press/twitter_directory.html\">Twitter帐号</a>，YouTube的<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/google\">官方频道</a>，等等。也许他们需要一个更能协调内部外部资源，能够制定企业的社交媒体战略的人。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://news.ccidnet.com/art/11099/20100512/2056821_1.html\">Google向社会公开招聘社交媒体业务主管</a>:</p>\n<blockquote><p>据科技网站GigaOm报道，Google正在与猎头公司商讨公开向社会招聘“社交媒体业务主管”候选人。虽然Google尚未确认这一消息，但自从Google在2009年下半年决定实施社交媒体战略后，已经陆续招聘了一批新的”社交网络团队”成员。 </p></blockquote>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/3885884-3076439044228588743?l=log.keso.cn\" alt=\"\"></div>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feed.keso.cn/~ff/kesoonblogger?a=KDPjMaa-F_4:3Z79gZo7H_Y:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/kesoonblogger?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\"></a> <a href=\"http://feed.keso.cn/~ff/kesoonblogger?a=KDPjMaa-F_4:3Z79gZo7H_Y:I9og5sOYxJI\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/kesoonblogger?d=I9og5sOYxJI\" border=\"0\"></a> <a href=\"http://feed.keso.cn/~ff/kesoonblogger?a=KDPjMaa-F_4:3Z79gZo7H_Y:clraHZBW0_I\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/kesoonblogger?d=clraHZBW0_I\" border=\"0\"></a> <a href=\"http://feed.keso.cn/~ff/kesoonblogger?a=KDPjMaa-F_4:3Z79gZo7H_Y:F7zBnMyn0Lo\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/kesoonblogger?i=KDPjMaa-F_4:3Z79gZo7H_Y:F7zBnMyn0Lo\" border=\"0\"></a>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/kesoonblogger/~4/KDPjMaa-F_4\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\"></p>\n","author":197,"categories":[20534],"tags":[5908,10436,8339,3764]}